<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Work With Us</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/fonts.css">

    <style>

		:root {
			--primary: #C4A97D;
			--secondary: #3A3A3A;
			--accent: #C4A97D;
			--accent-light: #A0845C;
			--bg: #1A1A1A;
			--bg-warm: #2A2A2A;
			--border: #444444;
			--text: #F0F0F0;
			--text-light: #B0B0B0;
		}

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Vazirmatn', sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        /* ============================== */
        /* MAIN */
        /* ============================== */
        main {
            padding: 0 5rem;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        main h1 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary);
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-top: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }

        main>p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
            max-width: 700px;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        /* ============================== */
        /* SECTION */
        /* ============================== */
        section {
            margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
        }

        section h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        /* ============================== */
        /* LISTS */
        /* ============================== */
        ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        ul li {
            background: var(--bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: var(--text);
            transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;
            border-radius: 0;
        }

        ul li:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, .04);
        }

        /* ============================== */
        /* CONTACT INFO */
        /* ============================== */
        .contact-info {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }

        .contact-item {
            background: var(--bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem;
            transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;
        }

        .contact-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, .04);
        }

        .contact-item strong {
            display: block;
            color: var(--primary);
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
        }

        .contact-item span {
            color: var(--text-light);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* ============================== */
        /* RESPONSIVE */
        /* ============================== */
        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            main {
                padding: 0 2rem;
            }
            main h1 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
                margin-top: 3rem;
            }
            .contact-info {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
            ul {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            main {
                padding: 0 1.2rem;
            }
            main h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
                margin-top: 2rem;
            }
            main>p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            .contact-info {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            section h2 {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
            }
            ul li {
                padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }
            .contact-item {
                padding: 1rem 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>

</head>
<body>

    <!-- ============================== -->
    <!-- HEADER: Include header partial -->
    <!-- ============================== -->
    <%- include('./partials/headerEnNi.ejs') %>

    <!-- ============================== -->
    <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
    <!-- ============================== -->
    <main>

        <!-- Page title -->
        <h1>Work With Us</h1>

        <!-- Introduction paragraph -->
        <p>
            We are open to collaboration proposals, project outsourcing, and partnership agreements in our areas of expertise. Here you can learn about how we work and the benefits of partnering with us.
        </p>

        <!-- ============================== -->
        <!-- SECTION 1: Benefits -->
        <!-- ============================== -->
        <section>
            <h2>Benefits of Outsourcing & Working With Us</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Quality guarantee and on-time project delivery</li>
                <li>Access to a skilled and experienced team</li>
                <li>Technical support and consultation throughout the contract</li>
                <li>Transparency in processes and regular reporting</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- ============================== -->
        <!-- SECTION 2: Process & Conditions -->
        <!-- ============================== -->
        <section>
            <h2>Process & Contract Conditions</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Initial project needs assessment and free consultation</li>
                <li>Transparent technical and financial proposal</li>
                <li>Official contract signing and execution phase planning</li>
                <li>Commitment to information confidentiality (NDA)</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- ============================== -->
        <!-- SECTION 3: Contact Information -->
        <!-- ============================== -->
        <section>
            <h2>Direct Contact Information</h2>
            <div class="contact-info">
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <strong>Business Unit Email</strong>
                    <span>partners@example.com</span>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <strong>Contracts Department Phone</strong>
                    <span>+98 900 000 0000</span>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <strong>Head Office Address</strong>
                    <span>Tehran, Iran</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <!-- ============================== -->
    <!-- FOOTER: Include footer partial -->
    <!-- ============================== -->
    <%- include('./partials/footerEnNi.ejs') %>

</body>
</html>